class disk_analyzer.model_pipeline.model_pipeline.ModelPipeline(data_paths: List[str] | None = None, train_test_splitter: TrainTestSplitter | None = None, data_preprocessor: DataPreprocessor | None = None, model_scorer: ModelScorer | None = None, rm_truncated_from_test: bool = True, batchsize: int = 500000, prep_storage_path: str = './Data/preprocessed', model_params: Dict | None = None)[source]

Bases: object

Class that incorporates all pipeline logic Consists of the following stages:

  1. Data Preprocessor: split data into train and test, preprocess data

  2. Model: train and predict

  3. Scoring: get metrics
